{
  "stem": "25809.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was [INAUDIBLE], Let me give that in English.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] 106, 108.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, yes-- usually after school, I would go to the, to the store, because my father wanted me to work in the store.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As young as I was, he had always things for me to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That I do not recall at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a fair amount of Jewish people, of course, in those days living in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a big, a big Jewish community in Amsterdam, very big.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, most of them disappeared during the Nazi occupation and, and, and the aftermath of that and the result of that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that would be difficult for me to do because of my-- I was only six, seven years old, so--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What impressed me was the, the Yiddish speaking, which, strangely enough, I didn't really care that much for.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was totally unaware of-- you see, my, my parents never paid much attention to me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe it was that when I was in that area, that they paid a lot more attention to children than my parents paid to me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it almost felt embarrassing to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe that was the reason.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was much more kindness, actually, in the ghetto, though it wasn't a closed off ghetto like in other cities.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a total open area, but the area where a lot of Jewish people would congregate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I think the only reason why we came there, because on occasion, maybe we wanted some kosher meat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe that's the only reason how I got there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I still can totally picture, as young as I was at the time, the butchery shop where we would buy some meat.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's not much to tell.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
